, sans oublier le bien-être psychique qu’apporte le plaisir de manger un aliment qui est bon et qu’on aime.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn French.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 24. Apr 2022) 0aChocolatexTherapeutic use. 4aNutrition. 7aMEDICAL / Nutrition.2bisacsh08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEDP Sciences Backlist eBook Package 2001 - 2015z978311075641840uhttps://doi.org/10.1051/978-2-7598-1295-040uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9782759812950423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9782759812950/original  a978-3-11-075641-8  EDP Sciences Backlist eBook Package 2001 - 2015c2001d2015  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_CL_MDPM  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_PPALL  aEBA_STMALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA12STME  aPDA5EBK